text: Buchen is a town in Neckar-Odenwald district, Baden-Württemberg, Germany. Buchen may also refer to: *Büchen, a municipality in the district of Lauenburg, Schleswig-Holstein, Germany *Büchen (Amt), a collective municipality in the district of Lauenburg, Schleswig-Holstein, Germany *Gustave W. Buchen (1886–1951), American politician and attorney, Wisconsin State Senator *Philip W. Buchen (1916–2001), American attorney and White House Counsel during the Ford administration
